PurgeActionDefinitionContext is a Form
    title is "PurgeActionDefinition"
    Layout
        paragraph
            BusinessView
                raise yellow alert when (DisplayBCYellowAlert)
                    mouse over text is untranslatable:"<BCYellowAlertMessage>"
            BusinessAction
        paragraph
            Description
                use text area of 5 lines
        paragraph
            Inactive
            ArchivingEnabled
                raise red alert when (not ArchivingEnabled)
                    mouse over text is "ArchivingIsNotEnabled"
                raise yellow alert when (DisplayYellowAlert)
                    mouse over text is untranslatable:"<OtherYellowAlertMessage>"
            valid when (DeveloperMode)
                Delivered
